channel.title: mycatalog updates
channel.description: 'My Catalog' uses the IBM Cloud catalog API to retrieve data from the catalog. It attempts to be as accurate as possible. This feed shows additions, updates, removals from the catalog. Use with care. It is a work-in-progress :)

item.title: [updated] Planning Analytics (planning-analytics) has changed the description of the plan named enterprise
item.description: *before*: This is a quota based subscription plan for Planning Analytics SaaS deployed on AWS. A base instance includes 10 Authorized Users, 48GB of Memory and 512GB of storage., *after*: This is a quota-based plan.
